    "Html": "\r\n<p>Hi,</p>\r\n<p>I am trying to capture this key event in my datagrid preview key down...but all that i get is a windows system sound. My other key events are ok. Can I use ALT &#43; Keys shortcuts with the WPF datagrid??<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">private</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">void</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"> dgPa_PreviewKeyDown(</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-size:x-small\">object</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">\r\n sender, </span><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">KeyEventArgs</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"> e)</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">if (e.Key == </span><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">Key</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">.A &amp;&amp;\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">Keyboard</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">.Modifiers ==\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:x-small\">ModifierKeys</span></span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">.Alt)<br>\r\n{&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\r\n}</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:xx-small\">}</span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n",
